{"id":"07ef0c56c60f1b4fdca4698b28fbff7c32f9a479ffcdcd7c0f829ad0f5927e48","item_id":"d4a23e66c6:0","text":"生成一种颜色，表示理想黑体在给定温度下被加热后，于可见光谱中发出的辐射。这样可以基于标准温度度量轻松创建可信的灯光颜色。"}
{"item_id":"d4a23e66c6:1","text":"Input Parameters（输入参数）"}
{"id":"b958ce8b871ab36b3ceee0e0f012b6182962b2db7926be0a670149f9fbd00b84","item_id":"d4a23e66c6:2","text":"Temperature（温度）"}
{"id":"5ce7df041c34b68552d501368663cb3b96b7643d4ea4c607bd6ab6bc62bbd672","item_id":"d4a23e66c6:3","text":"黑体的温度（单位为 kelvin）。Color temperatures（色温）超过 5,000K 时称为 cool colors（冷色，偏蓝白），较低的色温（2,700 到 3,000 K）称为 warm colors（暖色，从偏黄白到红色）。"}
{"id":"171ef9140267b2097f83844ccfcd92d6acecf7ff71943eaf02d6fa35d003d674","item_id":"d4a23e66c6:4","text":"上图：从 1,000K 到 6,500K 的线性渐变，exposure 为 -22。下图：从 5,000K 到 15,000K 的线性渐变，exposure 为 -28。"}
{"id":"2165909b54c15a440ee80baf7077a35f677c8c40514514a60eec5b275ee8dfae","item_id":"d4a23e66c6:5","text":"Temperature Value（温度值）"}
{"id":"0e570ca6fabe24f94e52c1833f3ffd25567022beb826fa16891f3322051bc221","item_id":"d4a23e66c6:6","text":"光源"}
{"id":"0a285d3e3b1ff7d2ff746ff6b45a48681e55083f5450b13f75fed6149e5b1421","item_id":"d4a23e66c6:7","text":"火柴火焰"}
{"id":"8df1214871f0f58433e62c5bed442e1a07a7af26b6f88e17acc0b37009fe5b4a","item_id":"d4a23e66c6:8","text":"蜡烛火焰、日落/日出"}
{"id":"ba5b702a04deab02da764543f1fb50a64489403af2f41e63340962f3694006e3","item_id":"d4a23e66c6:9","text":"2700 到 3300"}
{"id":"4bd9e4d2c9cb5fa710d9b9062cede29c2f4d6f4ae28d7dcfba57323fedef784d","item_id":"d4a23e66c6:10","text":"白炽灯"}
{"id":"fb9568174a7a8b0c2bfa1bc875ff38de9c0aeb082fdb3c9ea3b17b6d838f366e","item_id":"d4a23e66c6:11","text":"柔和（或暖）白紧凑型荧光灯"}
{"id":"56585230a2767ae86ef7d5673f3077650106e695f99495674a59335ecbf53528","item_id":"d4a23e66c6:12","text":"摄影棚灯、泛光摄影灯等"}
{"id":"94359696d4dc746633fb788548088eecafda637fae1ca9cfc931c8add2ddca2d","item_id":"d4a23e66c6:13","text":"摄影棚 CP 灯"}
